 {"id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5.2","title":"[T2-PROD.2] fcp.confluence — Atlassian Confluence Wiki Connector","description":"Confluence wiki connector, pairing with our existing Jira connector for full Atlassian coverage. Operations: confluence.pages.get, confluence.pages.list, confluence.pages.create, confluence.pages.update, confluence.pages.delete; confluence.spaces.list, confluence.spaces.get; confluence.search (CQL query); confluence.comments.list, confluence.comments.create; confluence.attachments.list, confluence.attachments.upload. Auth: Atlassian API token (email + token) or OAuth2. Network: *.atlassian.net. REST API v2. Page create/update=Risky, delete=Dangerous, reads=Safe. 3 subtasks.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:01:12.304201Z","created_by":"jemanuel","updated_at":"2026-03-18T00:25:06.487913Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5.2","depends_on_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:01:12.304201Z","created_by":"jemanuel","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":1801,"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5.2","author":"jemanuel","text":"Testing requirements: 50+ unit tests (wiremock), 10+ integration tests (ConnectorSuite/ComplianceSuite), E2E compliance script, structured JSON logging with connector_id/operation_id/duration_ms, retry telemetry with attempt/delay_ms/error. All tests deterministic, no real API calls, no timing-based flakiness.","created_at":"2026-03-18T00:25:06Z"}]}
