 {"id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5.3","title":"[T2-PROD.3] fcp.coda — Coda Document Platform Connector","description":"Coda doc/spreadsheet/app hybrid connector. Operations: coda.docs.list, coda.docs.get, coda.docs.create; coda.tables.list, coda.tables.get; coda.rows.list, coda.rows.upsert, coda.rows.delete; coda.formulas.list, coda.formulas.get; coda.controls.list, coda.controls.get; coda.pages.list, coda.pages.get. Auth: API token (Bearer). Network: coda.io. REST API v1. Row upsert=Risky, doc create=Risky, delete=Dangerous, reads=Safe. 3 subtasks.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:01:25.336377Z","created_by":"jemanuel","updated_at":"2026-03-18T00:25:06.797798Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5.3","depends_on_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:01:25.336377Z","created_by":"jemanuel","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":1802,"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.5.3","author":"jemanuel","text":"Testing requirements: 50+ unit tests (wiremock), 10+ integration tests (ConnectorSuite/ComplianceSuite), E2E compliance script, structured JSON logging with connector_id/operation_id/duration_ms, retry telemetry with attempt/delay_ms/error. All tests deterministic, no real API calls, no timing-based flakiness.","created_at":"2026-03-18T00:25:06Z"}]}
